BulkUpdateScalingFactorsTest
├── When caller is not Fee Manager
│   └── It should revert with "NFM"
└── When caller is Fee Manager
    ├── When pools array and scaling factors array are not the same length
    │   └── It should revert with "LMM"
    └── When pools array and scaling factors array are the same length
        ├── When one of the pools is invalid
        │   └── It should revert
        └── When all pools are valid
            ├── When one of the pools fee cap is not set
            │   └── It should revert with "ISF"
            └── When all the pools have a set fee cap
                ├── When one of scaling factor is bigger than max scaling factor
                │   └── It should revert with "ISF"
                └── When all the scaling factors are below max scaling factor
                    ├── It should update the scaling factor for all the pools
                    └── It should emit a {ScalingFactorSet} event for all the pools